defaultWhat progress is the government making on reducing the demadefaultnd for heat?default&#xa0;
defaultWe recognise Government efforts to promote heat reduction, and believe that positive steps for the delivery of heat demand reduction have been made. The production of the strategy documents for Heat and for Energy 
